## Quick Start Guide

### 1. Clone the Repository
To clone this forked repository locally, execute the following command:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/JBavaji/practise-mcino-Introduction-to-Git-and-GitHub.git
cd practise-mcino-Introduction-to-Git-and-GitHub
```

